page.title: 14Living In Keynsham In 1985
page.content: {In 1985 some people have videos and} computers.I have a computer,it is the Acorn Electron.The games I have are, Sphinx-Adventure,Snapper,Boxer and Desk Diary.I have a video with ten tapes,and one of them is a test tape. We tape lots of things like films, cartoons,and quizes.I like the carto -ons because they are funny.My brot -hers and I have a tape called Children's One.My mum and dad have a tape called Adult Two.I have a cat called called Bonny.She is ninety -eight if you count in cat years.She is black and white.On Monday I go to Brownies,and I am a Sixer.We do lots of challenges such as miming,when you have to mime an act.I go to dancing on Tuesdays and we dance to Mrs Veale.I like it very much.On Sundays I go to Sunday School,and mt teacher is called Bob.
